---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy – Solar Panel Calculator"
  description="Privacy policy for Solar Panel Calculator: what data we collect, how we use it, and your rights."
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-500">Last updated: July 8, 2026</p>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-8 leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Overview</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          Solar Panel Calculator ("we", "us") operates this website to provide free solar
          estimation tools. This policy explains what information we collect and how we use it.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Calculator inputs</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          Values you enter into the calculators (electricity bill, rates, roof area, and similar)
          are processed entirely in your browser. They are not transmitted to or stored on our
          servers.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Contact form</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          If you submit the contact form, we collect the details you provide (name, email, and
          message) solely to respond to your inquiry. We do not sell your personal information.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Advertising, analytics, and cookies</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          This site is supported by advertising. We may use Google AdSense to display ads, and
          analytics tools (such as Google Analytics or Microsoft Clarity) to understand aggregate
          site usage. These services may set cookies and, where you consent, use them to
          personalize ads.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          Advertising and analytics cookies are only set after you accept them in the cookie
          banner. You can change your choice at any time via the "Cookie Settings" link in the
          footer, and you can additionally opt out of personalized advertising in
          <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" class="text-brand-700 underline" rel="noopener nofollow">Google Ads Settings</a>.
          Declining cookies does not limit access to any calculator or article.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Third-party links</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          This site may link to third-party websites, including solar installers and product
          retailers. We are not responsible for their privacy practices.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Your rights</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of the personal information you
          submitted through our forms by contacting us via the <a href="/contact/" class="text-brand-700 underline">contact page</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          We may update this policy from time to time. Material changes will be reflected in the
          "Last updated" date above.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
